name: Startup Website Structure Guide
description:
The contents of this guide are designed to help anyone; especially new designers to make sense the structure of their design or in need of some inspiring content to get the best out of a design challenge for a startup website.


Included

  • Home Page


Prototype link


Since creating this, I have spent most of my time grasping all of Figma's new updates, and I would love to showcase a few things I've learnt so far.


However, I have decided to stay focused on concept behind this resource and only make relevant additions, and in order to narrow my focus, I would be thrilled to hear what members of the community would like to see in the next set of updates to this resource.
